                                    "content": "Bayeux handshake request sent to the transient `*.rt.yammer.com` relay host returned by\n`RealtimeConnectionSettingsClients`.\n\nThe captured admin session sent redacted `token` and `hub_tenant_token` values in the\nhandshake `ext` payload instead of using `Authorization` or cookie headers.\n",
